title: >>> Two GAMES in One
body_text:
The most unique logo in dodgeball history has been released!
It's a game within itself: a word search!
Complete the puzzle if you can!
*Words go frontwards, backwards, vertical, horizontal, and diagonal*
What more could we expect come DODGEBALL TWENTY-TWO?
The only way to find out is to be there live this coming Saturday, the 14th!
DODGEBALL TWENTY-TWO starts at 7PM ET.
